The '''''Manticore Squadron''''' was a group of [[Delta-class JV-7 escort shuttle]]s, attendant to the [[Dreadnaught-class heavy cruiser/Legends|Dreadnaught]] [[VTR-LX|''VTR-LX1'']], that was on its way to a penal station and carrying Rebel prisoners of war.

